title: “This is what your safe vaccine has done to me” | Real Climate Science
cleaned_text:
“I’m a 48 year old man, multiple blood clots in my lungs,

 ventricular tachycardia, wide spread vascular neuropathy, I require care takers to wash me, and cook for me. Before your vaccine, I had a successful career, I was healthy. This is what your ‘safe’ vaccine has done to me.”
